import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz'
import Dropdown from '../app/components/dropdown'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"dropdown-for-units"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#dropdown-for-units"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Dropdown for units`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"properties-table"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#properties-table"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Properties Table`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={Dropdown} />
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"playground"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#playground"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Playground`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={1} __code={`<Dropdown
  options={[{ label: \'wei\', value: \'18\' }, { label: \'ether\', value: \'1\' }]}
/>`} __scope={{props,Dropdown}}>
      <Dropdown options={[{label:'wei', value:'18'},{label:'ether', value:'1'}]} />
</Playground></MDXTag>
